{"tid":2461431,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"21歲仔，做地產年薪過百，你問我答","createTime":"2021-03-25T11:52:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T11:55:38.000Z","uid":28449,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"be06bf666a3f6d6b85d1a45b067b9b59db890679","tid":2461431,"uid":28449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T11:52:05.000Z","msg":"2018年入行，經歷過中美貿易，社會運動，疫情<br />\n市道吾算好的情況下，上年搵年薪過百。<br />\n<br />\n可能係運氣，可能係命運，但我相信天道酬勤，默默學習付出，因為係地產界，我身邊都好多人一單發達，靠運搵食。<br />\n<br />\n自己做左三年，每年生意上都有突破，我自己覺得，第一步，選擇最重要，擇啱人帶你入行，傳承功夫，第二，虛心學習，吾好有心魔，一直堅持付出，第三，檢討自己，呢行好多人突破吾到上限，都係覺得自己搵夠，冇去反省自己問題，搵客跟客簽單，每一小環都好重要，環環相扣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n歡迎交流入行<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/hUa8JOf1eAMzMTU9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FhUa8JOf1eAMzMTU9&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2Fspe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=9cb1044e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/hUa8JOf1eAMzMTU9</a>"},{"pid":"ade6d116b32206b4e6295f251aedf16a0c0fa6b9","tid":2461431,"uid":23019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T11:54:20.000Z","msg":"年薪過百每個月都有十蚊wo,幾叻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e981c805bf9b8cc634b3b61e160b8bc25e191dea","tid":2461431,"uid":66283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T11:54:37.000Z","msg":"有冇試過為咗搶單同人打交？"},{"pid":"afc52978d543963d560b905a722846639964a78b","tid":2461431,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T11:54:38.000Z","msg":"樓主啱啱入行上頭叫佢搵下線<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc2e9e3c33aeecb0a4e3b73b225a0108e36215b","tid":2461431,"uid":84037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be06bf666a3f6d6b85d1a45b067b9b59db890679","tid":2461431,"uid":28449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"